 🎨 Color Detection using Pandas

 📌 Project Overview

This project is a **Color Detection Application** built using **Python**, **OpenCV** and **Pandas**. It detects the color of any pixel in an image when the user double-clicks on it. The application displays the closest matching color name along with its RGB values.

The project uses a CSV dataset containing color names and RGB values, which is loaded using the Pandas library.

---

## 🚀 Features

* Detects the nearest color from an image.
* Displays:

  * Color Name
  * Red (R) Value
  * Green (G) Value
  * Blue (B) Value
* Interactive mouse double-click event.
* Uses OpenCV for image processing.
* Uses Pandas to read and manage the color dataset.

---

